This diagram gives a high-level overview of the way the operational simulation model generates and processes calls.
Remember - it's impossible for the model to perfectly capture all of the complexity of a real system, and simplications have to be made. However, extensive testing has been undertaken to confirm that, even with these simplifications and assumptions in place, the model provides a good reflection of the real world data we have observed over several years.
